# SECTION 4: Structural Diagrams & Schematics

## 4.1 Block-Level Architecture Flow — Dual-Layer Validation Pipeline

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[User opens register.html] --> B[Browser renders HTML form]
    B --> C[User fills five input fields]
    C --> D{User clicks Register button}
    D -->|onsubmit event fires| E[JavaScript validateForm runs]
    E --> F{All fields pass JS checks?}
    F -->|No| G[Display red error messages in spans]
    G --> H[event.preventDefault blocks submission]
    H --> I[Form remains on page - user fixes input]
    I --> C
    F -->|Yes| J[Browser sends HTTP POST to process.php]
    J --> K[Apache web server receives request]
    K --> L[PHP engine executes process.php]
    L --> M{PHP re-validates all fields}
    M -->|No| N[Aggregate errors into array]
    N --> O[Render red error list - echo HTML]
    M -->|Yes| P[Sanitize data with htmlspecialchars]
    P --> Q[Display green success message]
    Q --> R[Optional: INSERT into MySQL database]
    R --> S[Send response back to browser]
    O --> S
    S --> T[Browser displays final result page]
```

## 4.2 State Machine — Validation Field States

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Empty
    Empty --> Validating: User types first character
    Validating --> Empty: User clears field
    Validating --> Invalid: Fails regex or length check
    Validating --> Valid: Passes all checks
    Invalid --> Validating: User edits field
    Valid --> Validating: User edits field again
    Valid --> Submitted: All fields valid and form submitted
    Invalid --> SubmittedBlocked: Submission halted by preventDefault
    Submitted --> [*]
    SubmittedBlocked --> Validating
```

## 4.3 Component Interaction Diagram

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph Client_Browser
        A1[HTML Form] --> A2[DOM Elements]
        A2 --> A3[JavaScript Engine]
        A3 --> A4[validate.js script]
        A4 --> A5[Regex Tester]
    end
    subgraph Web_Server
        B1[Apache HTTP Server] --> B2[PHP Interpreter]
        B2 --> B3[process.php]
        B3 --> B4[preg_match / filter_var]
        B4 --> B5[Error Aggregator]
    end
    A3 -->|HTTP POST form data| B1
    B2 -->|HTTP Response HTML| A1
    A4 -. Optional: AJAX .-> B2
    B5 --> B6[Output: Success or Error List]
```

## 4.4 File Dependency Map

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    F1[register.html] -->|loads script src| F2[validate.js]
    F1 -->|form action POST| F3[process.php]
    F2 -->|reads input values| F4[DOM Input Elements]
    F2 -->|writes error text| F5[Span Error Elements]
    F3 -->|reads| F6[POST superglobal]
    F3 -->|executes| F7[preg_match and filter_var]
    F3 -->|outputs| F8[HTML response page]
```
