### Question B (14 Marks — Alternative Choice) **[KTU University Exam - June 2023]**

**(a)** Explain **regular expressions** in JavaScript. Write a JavaScript program that uses regex to validate a user-entered **email address** and **Indian mobile number**. Display inline error messages. **(7 marks)**

**(b)** Discuss the importance of **server-side validation in PHP**. Write a PHP script that validates a **username and password** received via `$_POST`, ensuring the username is alphanumeric (3–20 chars) and the password is at least 8 characters with at least one uppercase, one lowercase, and one digit. **(7 marks)**

