### **Question A (14 Marks) [KTU University Exam – July 2024, Model]**

**(a)** Explain the three methods of applying CSS to an HTML document with suitable examples. Discuss CSS specificity with a proper specificity calculation example. **(7 marks)**

**(b)** Write a complete JavaScript program that validates a registration form containing the fields: **Name, Email, Password, Confirm Password, Phone (10 digits)**. The validation must occur *before* the form is submitted to the server. Show error messages inline next to each field. **(7 marks)**

